reviewText: ok one thing, if you listen to the English dub the guys name sounds like Sky but if you look at the back cover the guys name is Sora. in this volume we see the nurse/ researcher Hiyori Kisaragi. she a kinky girl with a Lolita look and she wants Sora to play with her. ow if you pay attention to when Hiyori goes to video store she buys other volumes of night shift nurses.
